BalanceForwardRuleHelper
public static class BalanceForwardRuleHelper.BalanceForwardProcessState
extends Object

A container for the state of the balance forward process. The way state is handled is heavily dependent upon the way in which YearEndServiceImpl.forwardBalancesForFiscalYear works.
